{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-24-3",
 "title": "Recruiting the Slicer",
 "summary": "Landing the weary Triton at the Coruscant Imperial City spaceport, the disguised NRI agent Bazil McKenzie (as Mege Vauki) arrives to collect a technician he has been ordered to add to his team. The man, Marcus Delvennis, has been waiting for him and amusingly reveals his own New Republic ID, sparing Bazil the trouble of searching. Over a shared cup of caf, Bazil explains the mission and Marcus, a self-described \"tech in disguise,\" eagerly signs on to slice into Imperial systems. When Bazil reveals their target is the new Death Star that destroyed Gastus a week earlier, the shocked Marcus sobers but commits to retrieving its plans. With the rest of the team asleep and a long flight into Imperial space ahead, Bazil leads the new recruit aboard to rest before departure.",
